<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَبُوهُ وَعُمْرُهُ في الثَّدْيِ عَامُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَقَدْ يحْلُو لَهُ التَّسْبِيحُ لَيْلاً<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَيُوقِظُني وَقَدْ نَامَ الأَنَامُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>رُوَيْدَاً أَيُّهَا الرَّجُلُ الصَّغِيرُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَمَا أَدَبٌ لَدَيْكَ وَلاَ احْتِشَامُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>تُبَخِّرُني بِعِطْرِكَ كُلَّ يَوْمٍ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَعِطْرُكَ ذَا الصَّلاَةُ بِهِ حَرَامُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>هَدَايَاكَ الثَّمِينَةُ أَحْرَجَتْني<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَضَاعَ بِهَا الْوَقَارُ وَالاِحْتِرَامُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c3">{شِعْر / عِصَام الْغَزَالي بِتَصَرُّف}</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>مُتْعَةُ السَّفَرِ بِالْقِطَار <span class="c4">[- رضي الله عنه -]</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أُفَضِّلُ أَن أُسَافِرَ بِالْقِطَارِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>يَشُقُّ طَرِيقَهُ بَينَ الصَّحَارِي<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>أُحِبُّ رُكُوبَهُ مِن غَيْرِ شَرْطٍ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>أَبِالْبَنْزِينِ سَارَ أَمِ الْبُخَارِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>مُشَاهَدَةُ الحُقُولِ بِجَانِبَيْهِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>شِفَاءٌ لِلصِّغَارِ وَلِلْكِبَارِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>تَرَاهُ مُسْرِعَاً دَوْمَاً كَلِصٍّ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>يَلُوذُ مِنَ الحُكُوَمَةِ بِالْفِرَارِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَيَجْرِي فَوْقَ خَطٍّ مُسْتَقِيمٍ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>